<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>MSG-Embedding 平台 · 5G NR 信道数据工厂与模型评估引擎</title>
<style>
/* ========== RESET & BASE ========== */
*, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
html { scroll-behavior: smooth; font-size: 16px; }
body {
  font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', 'PingFang SC', 'Microsoft YaHei', sans-serif;
  background: #0a0e17;
  color: #e0e6ed;
  line-height: 1.7;
  overflow-x: hidden;
}
a { color: #60a5fa; text-decoration: none; }
a:hover { color: #93c5fd; }
code, .mono { font-family: 'Cascadia Code', 'Fira Code', 'JetBrains Mono', monospace; }

/* ========== ANIMATED BACKGROUND ========== */
.bg-grid {
  position: fixed; inset: 0; z-index: -2;
  background-image:
    linear-gradient(rgba(59,130,246,0.04) 1px, transparent 1px),
    linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(59,130,246,0.04) 1px, transparent 1px);
  background-size: 60px 60px;
  animation: gridDrift 20s linear infinite;
}
@keyframes gridDrift { to { background-position: 60px 60px; } }

.bg-glow {
  position: fixed; z-index: -1;
  width: 800px; height: 800px;
  border-radius: 50%;
  filter: blur(120px);
  opacity: 0.15;
  pointer-events: none;
}
.bg-glow--1 { top: -200px; left: -200px; background: #3b82f6; animation: float1 12s ease-in-out infinite; }
.bg-glow--2 { bottom: -300px; right: -200px; background: #8b5cf6; animation: float2 15s ease-in-out infinite; }
.bg-glow--3 { top: 40%; left: 50%; background: #06b6d4; animation: float3 18s ease-in-out infinite; }
@keyframes float1 { 50% { transform: translate(80px, 60px); } }
@keyframes float2 { 50% { transform: translate(-60px, -80px); } }
@keyframes float3 { 50% { transform: translate(-40px, 50px); } }

/* ========== SCROLL-REVEAL ========== */
.reveal {
  opacity: 0; transform: translateY(40px);
  transition: opacity 0.8s cubic-bezier(.16,1,.3,1), transform 0.8s cubic-bezier(.16,1,.3,1);
}
.reveal.visible { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
.reveal-delay-1 { transition-delay: 0.15s; }
.reveal-delay-2 { transition-delay: 0.3s; }
.reveal-delay-3 { transition-delay: 0.45s; }
.reveal-delay-4 { transition-delay: 0.6s; }

/* ========== NAV ========== */
nav {
  position: fixed; top: 0; left: 0; right: 0; z-index: 100;
  display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between;
  padding: 0 40px; height: 64px;
  background: rgba(10,14,23,0.85);
  backdrop-filter: blur(16px);
  border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
  transition: background 0.3s;
}
nav.scrolled { background: rgba(10,14,23,0.95); }
.nav-logo {
  font-size: 1.15rem; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: -0.5px;
  background: linear-gradient(135deg, #60a5fa, #a78bfa);
  -webkit-background-clip: text; -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
}
.nav-links { display: flex; gap: 20px; list-style: none; flex-wrap: wrap; }
.nav-links a {
  font-size: 0.78rem; color: #94a3b8;
  transition: color 0.2s; position: relative;
}
.nav-links a:hover, .nav-links a.active { color: #e0e6ed; }
.nav-links a::after {
  content: ''; position: absolute; bottom: -4px; left: 0; right: 0;
  height: 2px; background: #60a5fa;
  transform: scaleX(0); transform-origin: left;
  transition: transform 0.3s;
}
.nav-links a:hover::after, .nav-links a.active::after { transform: scaleX(1); }

/* ========== SECTIONS ========== */
section { padding: 100px 40px; max-width: 1200px; margin: 0 auto; }
section:first-of-type { padding-top: 160px; }

/* ========== HERO ========== */
.hero { text-align: center; padding-top: 200px; padding-bottom: 100px; }
.hero-badge {
  display: inline-block; padding: 6px 16px; border-radius: 20px;
  background: rgba(59,130,246,0.12); border: 1px solid rgba(59,130,246,0.25);
  font-size: 0.8rem; color: #60a5fa; margin-bottom: 24px;
  animation: badgePulse 3s ease-in-out infinite;
}
@keyframes badgePulse { 50% { box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(59,130,246,0.15); } }
.hero h1 {
  font-size: 3.2rem; font-weight: 800; letter-spacing: -1.5px;
  line-height: 1.15; margin-bottom: 20px;
  background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fff 0%, #94a3b8 100%);
  -webkit-background-clip: text; -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
}
.hero h1 .gradient-text {
  background: linear-gradient(135deg, #60a5fa, #a78bfa, #f472b6);
  -webkit-background-clip: text; -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
}
.hero .subtitle {
  font-size: 1.15rem; color: #94a3b8; max-width: 720px; margin: 0 auto 40px; line-height: 1.8;
}
.hero-stats { display: flex; justify-content: center; gap: 40px; margin-top: 40px; flex-wrap: wrap; }
.hero-stat { text-align: center; }
.hero-stat .number {
  font-size: 2.4rem; font-weight: 800;
  background: linear-gradient(135deg, #60a5fa, #a78bfa);
  -webkit-background-clip: text; -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
}
.hero-stat .label { font-size: 0.78rem; color: #64748b; margin-top: 4px; }

/* ========== HEADINGS ========== */
.section-label {
  display: inline-block; font-size: 0.72rem; font-weight: 600;
  text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 2px; color: #60a5fa;
  margin-bottom: 12px;
}
.section-title {
  font-size: 2rem; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: -0.8px;
  margin-bottom: 16px; color: #f1f5f9;
}
.section-desc { font-size: 0.95rem; color: #94a3b8; max-width: 640px; margin-bottom: 48px; }

/* ========== CARDS ========== */
.card-grid { display: grid; gap: 24px; }
.card-grid--2 { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); }
.card-grid--3 { grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); }
.card-grid--4 { grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr); }
@media (max-width: 900px) {
  .card-grid--3, .card-grid--4 { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); }
}
@media (max-width: 600px) {
  .card-grid--2, .card-grid--3, .card-grid--4 { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
}

.card {
  background: rgba(15,23,42,0.6);
  border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
  border-radius: 16px; padding: 32px;
  transition: transform 0.3s, box-shadow 0.3s, border-color 0.3s;
  position: relative; overflow: hidden;
}
.card:hover {
  transform: translateY(-4px);
  box-shadow: 0 20px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
  border-color: rgba(59,130,246,0.2);
}
.card::before {
  content: ''; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; right: 0; height: 3px;
  background: linear-gradient(90deg, #3b82f6, #8b5cf6);
  opacity: 0; transition: opacity 0.3s;
}
.card:hover::before { opacity: 1; }
.card-icon {
  width: 48px; height: 48px; border-radius: 12px;
  display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
  font-size: 1.5rem; margin-bottom: 16px;
}
.card-icon--blue { background: rgba(59,130,246,0.1); }
.card-icon--purple { background: rgba(139,92,246,0.1); }
.card-icon--cyan { background: rgba(6,182,212,0.1); }
.card-icon--green { background: rgba(34,197,94,0.1); }
.card-icon--amber { background: rgba(245,158,11,0.1); }
.card-icon--red { background: rgba(239,68,68,0.1); }
.card h3 { font-size: 1.05rem; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px; color: #f1f5f9; }
.card p { font-size: 0.88rem; color: #94a3b8; line-height: 1.65; }

/* ========== TAGS ========== */
.tag {
  display: inline-block; padding: 3px 10px; border-radius: 6px;
  font-size: 0.72rem; font-weight: 500;
  background: rgba(59,130,246,0.1); color: #60a5fa;
  border: 1px solid rgba(59,130,246,0.2);
}
.tag--purple { background: rgba(139,92,246,0.1); color: #a78bfa; border-color: rgba(139,92,246,0.2); }
.tag--cyan { background: rgba(6,182,212,0.1); color: #22d3ee; border-color: rgba(6,182,212,0.2); }
.tag--green { background: rgba(34,197,94,0.1); color: #4ade80; border-color: rgba(34,197,94,0.2); }
.tag--amber { background: rgba(245,158,11,0.1); color: #fbbf24; border-color: rgba(245,158,11,0.2); }
.tag--red { background: rgba(239,68,68,0.1); color: #f87171; border-color: rgba(239,68,68,0.2); }
.tag--pink { background: rgba(244,114,182,0.1); color: #f9a8d4; border-color: rgba(244,114,182,0.2); }
.tags { display: flex; gap: 8px; flex-wrap: wrap; margin-top: 12px; }

/* ========== DATA TABLE ========== */
.data-table-wrap {
  overflow-x: auto; border-radius: 12px;
  border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
}
table { width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; font-size: 0.82rem; }
thead { background: rgba(30,41,59,0.8); }
th {
  padding: 14px 16px; text-align: left; font-weight: 600;
  color: #94a3b8; border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
  white-space: nowrap;
}
td {
  padding: 12px 16px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.04);
  color: #cbd5e1;
}
tbody tr { transition: background 0.2s; }
tbody tr:hover { background: rgba(59,130,246,0.05); }

/* ========== ARCHITECTURE DIAGRAM ========== */
.arch-diagram {
  background: rgba(15,23,42,0.5);
  border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
  border-radius: 20px; padding: 40px 32px;
  position: relative; overflow: hidden;
}
.arch-row {
  display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
  gap: 12px; margin: 16px 0; flex-wrap: wrap;
}
.arch-box {
  padding: 12px 18px; border-radius: 10px;
  font-size: 0.8rem; font-weight: 600;
  border: 1px solid; text-align: center;
  min-width: 120px;
  transition: transform 0.3s, box-shadow 0.3s;
}
.arch-box:hover { transform: scale(1.05); box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(0,0,0,0.3); }
.arch-box--blue { background: rgba(59,130,246,0.12); border-color: rgba(59,130,246,0.3); color: #93c5fd; }
.arch-box--purple { background: rgba(139,92,246,0.12); border-color: rgba(139,92,246,0.3); color: #c4b5fd; }
.arch-box--cyan { background: rgba(6,182,212,0.12); border-color: rgba(6,182,212,0.3); color: #67e8f9; }
.arch-box--green { background: rgba(34,197,94,0.12); border-color: rgba(34,197,94,0.3); color: #86efac; }
.arch-box--amber { background: rgba(245,158,11,0.12); border-color: rgba(245,158,11,0.3); color: #fcd34d; }
.arch-box--pink { background: rgba(244,114,182,0.12); border-color: rgba(244,114,182,0.3); color: #f9a8d4; }
.arch-arrow { font-size: 1.3rem; color: #475569; }
.arch-arrow--down { display: block; text-align: center; font-size: 1.4rem; margin: 4px 0; color: #475569; }

/* ========== CODE BLOCKS ========== */
.code-block {
  background: rgba(15,23,42,0.8);
  border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
  border-radius: 10px; padding: 20px 24px;
  overflow-x: auto; font-size: 0.8rem;
  line-height: 1.7; margin: 16px 0;
  position: relative;
}
.code-block .lang-label {
  position: absolute; top: 8px; right: 12px;
  font-size: 0.65rem; color: #475569;
  text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 1px;
}
.code-block code { color: #e2e8f0; white-space: pre; }
.code-block .kw { color: #c084fc; }
.code-block .fn { color: #60a5fa; }
.code-block .str { color: #4ade80; }
.code-block .num { color: #fbbf24; }
.code-block .cm { color: #64748b; font-style: italic; }
.code-block .op { color: #f472b6; }

/* ========== FORMULA ========== */
.formula-block {
  background: rgba(15,23,42,0.6);
  border: 1px solid rgba(139,92,246,0.15);
  border-left: 3px solid #8b5cf6;
  border-radius: 0 10px 10px 0;
  padding: 20px 28px; margin: 16px 0;
  font-size: 1.05rem; color: #e2e8f0;
  overflow-x: auto;
}
.formula-block .formula-label {
  font-size: 0.7rem; color: #a78bfa;
  text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 1.5px;
  margin-bottom: 10px; display: block;
}
.formula {
  font-family: 'Cambria Math', 'Times New Roman', serif;
  font-size: 1.05em; color: #e2e8f0;
  letter-spacing: 0.3px;
}
.formula sub { font-size: 0.7em; vertical-align: sub; }
.formula sup { font-size: 0.7em; vertical-align: super; }
.formula .var { font-style: italic; color: #93c5fd; }
.formula .const { color: #fbbf24; }

/* ========== CHALLENGE CARDS ========== */
.challenge-card {
  background: rgba(15,23,42,0.6);
  border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
  border-radius: 16px; padding: 28px;
  margin-bottom: 24px;
  transition: border-color 0.3s;
}
.challenge-card:hover { border-color: rgba(59,130,246,0.2); }
.challenge-header {
  display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 12px; margin-bottom: 16px;
}
.challenge-id {
  background: rgba(239,68,68,0.15); color: #f87171;
  padding: 4px 10px; border-radius: 6px;
  font-size: 0.72rem; font-weight: 700;
}
.challenge-title { font-size: 1.05rem; font-weight: 600; color: #f1f5f9; }
.challenge-section { margin: 12px 0; }
.challenge-section-label {
  font-size: 0.72rem; font-weight: 600; text-transform: uppercase;
  letter-spacing: 1px; margin-bottom: 6px; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 6px;
}
.challenge-section-label.problem { color: #f87171; }
.challenge-section-label.cause { color: #fbbf24; }
.challenge-section-label.solution { color: #4ade80; }
.challenge-section-label.result { color: #60a5fa; }
.challenge-section p { font-size: 0.88rem; color: #94a3b8; }

/* ========== SVG DIAGRAMS ========== */
.svg-container {
  background: rgba(15,23,42,0.5);
  border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
  border-radius: 16px; padding: 24px;
  margin: 24px 0; overflow: hidden;
}
.svg-container svg { width: 100%; height: auto; display: block; }
.svg-container .svg-title {
  font-size: 0.8rem; color: #64748b; text-align: center;
  margin-top: 12px; letter-spacing: 0.5px;
}

/* ========== UI MOCKUP ========== */
.ui-mockup {
  background: rgba(15,23,42,0.5);
  border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
  border-radius: 16px; overflow: hidden; margin: 24px 0;
}
.ui-mockup-header {
  background: rgba(30,41,59,0.8);
  padding: 10px 16px; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px;
  border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
}
.ui-dot { width: 10px; height: 10px; border-radius: 50%; }
.ui-dot--r { background: #f87171; }
.ui-dot--y { background: #fbbf24; }
.ui-dot--g { background: #4ade80; }
.ui-mockup-title { font-size: 0.72rem; color: #64748b; margin-left: 8px; }
.ui-mockup-body { padding: 24px; }

/* ========== METRIC CARDS ========== */
.metric-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: 20px; }
@media (max-width: 800px) { .metric-grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); } }
.metric-card {
  background: rgba(15,23,42,0.6);
  border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
  border-radius: 14px; padding: 24px; text-align: center;
  transition: border-color 0.3s, transform 0.3s;
}
.metric-card:hover { border-color: rgba(59,130,246,0.2); transform: translateY(-2px); }
.metric-card .metric-name {
  font-size: 0.82rem; color: #64748b; margin-bottom: 8px;
  text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 1px;
}
.metric-card .metric-formula {
  font-family: 'Cambria Math', serif; font-size: 0.95rem; color: #e2e8f0;
  margin: 12px 0; min-height: 40px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
}
.metric-card .metric-desc {
  font-size: 0.78rem; color: #94a3b8; line-height: 1.5;
}

/* ========== TWO-COL LAYOUT ========== */
.two-col { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 32px; align-items: start; }
@media (max-width: 800px) { .two-col { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } }

/* ========== TRUST LAYERS ========== */
.trust-layer {
  border-left: 3px solid; padding: 24px 28px; margin-bottom: 24px;
  background: rgba(15,23,42,0.4); border-radius: 0 12px 12px 0;
}
.trust-layer--l1 { border-color: #3b82f6; }
.trust-layer--l2 { border-color: #8b5cf6; }
.trust-layer--l3 { border-color: #06b6d4; }
.trust-layer h4 { font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 8px; color: #f1f5f9; }
.trust-layer p { font-size: 0.88rem; color: #94a3b8; }

/* ========== MISC ========== */
.divider { height: 1px; background: rgba(255,255,255,0.06); margin: 48px 0; }
.highlight { color: #60a5fa; font-weight: 600; }
.highlight--green { color: #4ade80; }
.highlight--amber { color: #fbbf24; }
.highlight--purple { color: #a78bfa; }
.text-sm { font-size: 0.85rem; }
.text-xs { font-size: 0.75rem; }
.text-muted { color: #64748b; }
.mt-8 { margin-top: 8px; }
.mt-16 { margin-top: 16px; }
.mt-24 { margin-top: 24px; }
.mt-32 { margin-top: 32px; }
.mb-16 { margin-bottom: 16px; }
.mb-24 { margin-bottom: 24px; }
.flex-center { display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; }
.gap-8 { gap: 8px; }
.gap-16 { gap: 16px; }

/* ========== STEP INDICATOR ========== */
.steps { display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; gap: 0; margin: 24px 0; }
.step-item { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0; }
.step-num {
  width: 36px; height: 36px; border-radius: 50%;
  display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
  font-size: 0.82rem; font-weight: 700;
  background: rgba(59,130,246,0.15); color: #60a5fa;
  border: 2px solid rgba(59,130,246,0.3);
}
.step-num.active { background: #3b82f6; color: #fff; box-shadow: 0 0 16px rgba(59,130,246,0.4); }
.step-label { font-size: 0.72rem; color: #94a3b8; margin-left: 8px; margin-right: 16px; }
.step-line { width: 40px; height: 2px; background: rgba(59,130,246,0.2); margin: 0 4px; }

/* ========== TOKEN DIAGRAM ========== */
.token-strip {
  display: flex; gap: 4px; flex-wrap: wrap; margin: 16px 0;
}
.token-cell {
  flex: 0 0 auto; padding: 6px 10px; border-radius: 6px;
  font-size: 0.7rem; font-weight: 600; text-align: center;
  border: 1px solid; min-width: 60px;
  transition: transform 0.2s;
}
.token-cell:hover { transform: scale(1.08); }

/* Footer */
footer {
  text-align: center; padding: 60px 40px;
  border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
  font-size: 0.8rem; color: #475569;
}
</style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="bg-grid"></div>
<div class="bg-glow bg-glow--1"></div>
<div class="bg-glow bg-glow--2"></div>
<div class="bg-glow bg-glow--3"></div>

<!-- ========================= NAV ========================= -->
<nav id="navbar">
  <div class="nav-logo">MSG-Embedding</div>
  <ul class="nav-links">
    <li><a href="#hero">首页</a></li>
    <li><a href="#why">痛点</a></li>
    <li><a href="#arch">架构</a></li>
    <li><a href="#sources">数据源</a></li>
    <li><a href="#workflow">操作流程</a></li>
    <li><a href="#tokens">Token架构</a></li>
    <li><a href="#tech-deep">技术图解</a></li>
    <li><a href="#model">模型</a></li>
    <li><a href="#eval">评估</a></li>
    <li><a href="#challenges">工程实战</a></li>
    <li><a href="#trust">可信度</a></li>
  </ul>
</nav>

<!-- ========================= 1. HERO ========================= -->
<section class="hero" id="hero">
  <div class="reveal">
    <div class="hero-badge">5G NR Channel Intelligence Platform</div>
    <h1>MSG-Embedding<br><span class="gradient-text">信道数据工厂与模型评估引擎</span></h1>
    <p class="subtitle">
      从 3GPP 标准仿真、射线追踪到 MATLAB QuaDRiGa —— 三源融合的信道数据采集、16维Token特征提取、
      ChannelMAE 自监督训练与 6 维度标准化评估，一站式解决 5G NR 信道表征学习的数据与评估难题。
    </p>
  </div>
  <div class="hero-stats reveal reveal-delay-1">
    <div class="hero-stat">
      <div class="number"><span class="counter" data-target="3">0</span></div>
      <div class="label">异构数据源</div>
    </div>
    <div class="hero-stat">
      <div class="number"><span class="counter" data-target="16">0</span></div>
      <div class="label">维 Token 架构</div>
    </div>
    <div class="hero-stat">
      <div class="number"><span class="counter" data-target="6">0</span></div>
      <div class="label">评估指标维度</div>
    </div>
    <div class="hero-stat">
      <div class="number"><span class="counter" data-target="286">0</span>+</div>
      <div class="label">自动化测试</div>
    </div>
    <div class="hero-stat">
      <div class="number"><span class="counter" data-target="8">0</span></div>
      <div class="label">工程难题攻克</div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ========================= 2. WHY ========================= -->
<section id="why">
  <div class="reveal">
    <div class="section-label">Motivation</div>
    <h2 class="section-title">为什么需要这个平台？</h2>
    <p class="section-desc">5G NR 信道表征学习面临三大核心挑战，每一个都足以阻断研究进展。</p>
  </div>
  <div class="card-grid card-grid--3">
    <div class="card reveal reveal-delay-1">
      <div class="card-icon card-icon--red">&#x1F4C9;</div>
      <h3>信道数据严重匮乏</h3>
      <p>真实 5G 信道数据获取成本极高：需要基站设备、频谱授权、测试终端。公开数据集几乎为零，
        研究者只能依赖简化仿真，难以覆盖 UMa/UMi/InF/HSR 等多样场景。
        缺乏标准化的数据格式更使不同来源的数据无法互通。</p>
    </div>
    <div class="card reveal reveal-delay-2">
      <div class="card-icon card-icon--amber">&#x1F527;</div>
      <h3>数据来源割裂孤立</h3>
      <p>统计模型（TDL）快但缺空间细节；射线追踪（Sionna RT）精确但极慢且易失败；
        QuaDRiGa 物理保真度最高但依赖 MATLAB。三类工具接口各异、功率标定不一致、
        方向互易处理不同，无法直接混合使用。功率差异可达 10 万倍（<span class="highlight">F-004</span>）。</p>
    </div>
    <div class="card reveal reveal-delay-3">
      <div class="card-icon card-icon--purple">&#x1F4CA;</div>
      <h3>模型评估缺乏标准</h3>
      <p>信道 Embedding 质量如何衡量？传统分类准确率无法捕捉"嵌入空间连续性"和"邻域一致性"。
        缺少标准化的评估流程：测试集随机划分、指标选择不一、结果不可复现。
        没有统一基准，模型迭代就是盲人摸象。</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

