<!-- ========================= 4. DATA SOURCES ========================= -->
<section id="sources">
  <div class="reveal">
    <div class="section-label">Data Sources</div>
    <h2 class="section-title">三源融合的数据工厂</h2>
    <p class="section-desc">每种数据源各有所长，平台通过统一的 ChannelSample 合约让三者无缝互通。</p>
  </div>

  <div class="data-table-wrap reveal reveal-delay-1">
    <table>
      <thead>
        <tr>
          <th>维度</th>
          <th style="color:#93c5fd">Internal Sim (Python TDL)</th>
          <th style="color:#fcd34d">Sionna RT (射线追踪)</th>
          <th style="color:#86efac">QuaDRiGa Real (MATLAB)</th>
        </tr>
      </thead>
      <tbody>
        <tr>
          <td><strong>物理保真度</strong></td>
          <td>中 — 统计信道 (3GPP TDL)</td>
          <td>高 — 几何射线追踪</td>
          <td>最高 — 空间一致性信道</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td><strong>生成速度</strong></td>
          <td class="highlight--green">最快 (纯 Python/NumPy)</td>
          <td>慢 (GPU 光线计算)</td>
          <td>中等 (MATLAB Engine)</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td><strong>场景覆盖</strong></td>
          <td>UMa, UMi, InF, RMa, HSR</td>
          <td>自定义 3D 场景</td>
          <td>UMa, UMi, InF, RMa</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td><strong>干扰建模</strong></td>
          <td>TDL 多小区叠加</td>
          <td>RT + TDL 混合回退</td>
          <td>空间一致性多小区</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td><strong>移动性</strong></td>
          <td>Jakes 时域相关 (F-008)</td>
          <td>轨迹连续 + RT快照</td>
          <td>4种移动模式</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td><strong>路损模型</strong></td>
          <td>3GPP 38.901 §7.4.1</td>
          <td>射线路径衰减</td>
          <td>QuaDRiGa 内置</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td><strong>核心实现</strong></td>
          <td><code>internal_sim.py</code></td>
          <td><code>sionna_rt.py</code></td>
          <td><code>quadriga_real.py</code> + <code>main_multi.m</code></td>
        </tr>
      </tbody>
    </table>
  </div>

  <!-- Source deep dive cards -->
  <div class="card-grid card-grid--3 mt-32">
    <div class="card reveal reveal-delay-1">
      <h3 style="color:#93c5fd">Internal Sim 亮点</h3>
      <p>完全 Python 原生实现的 3GPP TDL 信道生成器，支持 Jakes Sum-of-Sinusoids 时域相关模型。
        相邻快照自相关从 <span class="highlight--red" style="color:#f87171">0.13</span> 提升至
        <span class="highlight--green">0.88</span>（F-008 修复），真实还原移动场景的衰落特性。</p>
      <div class="code-block mt-16">
        <span class="lang-label">Python</span>
        <code><span class="cm"># Jakes SoS: 连续时间轴实现时域相关</span>
t_axis = t_offset_s + np.arange(T) * T_sym
<span class="kw">for</span> n <span class="kw">in</span> range(N_sinusoids):
    phase += A_n * np.cos(<span class="num">2</span>*np.pi*f_d*t_axis*cos_theta_n + phi_n)</code>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="card reveal reveal-delay-2">
      <h3 style="color:#fcd34d">Sionna RT 亮点</h3>
      <p>射线追踪提供最精确的空间传播特性，但当遮挡严重时 RT 可能返回全零信道。
        平台实现了智能回退策略（F-006）：优先复用上一成功快照，仅首帧无历史时才降级到 TDL，
        保持时间序列连续性。</p>
      <div class="code-block mt-16">
        <span class="lang-label">Python</span>
        <code><span class="kw">if</span> last_rt_channels <span class="kw">is not</span> <span class="const">None</span>:
    h_all = last_rt_channels  <span class="cm"># 复用上一成功快照</span>
<span class="kw">else</span>:
    h_all = _compute_channels_tdl(...)  <span class="cm"># 仅首帧降级</span></code>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="card reveal reveal-delay-3">
      <h3 style="color:#86efac">QuaDRiGa Real 亮点</h3>
      <p>通过 MATLAB Engine 直接调用 QuaDRiGa 仿真核心，1600+ 行 MATLAB 管线覆盖拓扑生成、
        多小区信道、UL/DL 干扰注入。自包含部署（F-014），无需外部硬编码路径，
        开箱即用。</p>
      <div class="code-block mt-16">
        <span class="lang-label">MATLAB</span>
        <code><span class="cm">% 零速度保护：防止 QuaDRiGa 插值 Inf 崩溃</span>
s1.set_speed(max(ue_speed_kmh, <span class="num">1e-3</span>), T_snapshots);
<span class="cm">% 快照不足时复制首帧填充</span>
<span class="kw">if</span> actual_ss < no_ss
    Hf_temp = repmat(Hf_temp(:,:,:,<span class="num">1</span>), [<span class="num">1 1 1</span> no_ss]);
<span class="kw">end</span></code>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

