        <div class="svg-title">高铁场景：线性基站部署、列车穿透损耗建模、速度自适应 Doppler</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- STEP 2: Data Processing -->
  <div class="reveal mt-32">
    <h3 style="color:#f1f5f9; font-size:1.1rem; margin-bottom:16px;">
      <span class="tag tag--cyan">Step 2</span> &nbsp;Bridge 特征处理流水线
    </h3>
    <div class="ui-mockup">
      <div class="ui-mockup-header">
        <div class="ui-dot ui-dot--r"></div>
        <div class="ui-dot ui-dot--y"></div>
        <div class="ui-dot ui-dot--g"></div>
        <div class="ui-mockup-title">MSG Platform — 数据处理</div>
      </div>
      <div class="ui-mockup-body">
        <div class="arch-row" style="margin-bottom:24px">
          <div class="arch-box arch-box--purple">ChannelSample<br><span style="font-size:0.7rem;opacity:0.7">[T,RB,BS,UE] complex64</span></div>
          <span class="arch-arrow">&#x2192;</span>
          <div class="arch-box arch-box--cyan">Bridge 特征提取<br><span style="font-size:0.7rem;opacity:0.7">SVD · DFT · PDP · RSRP</span></div>
          <span class="arch-arrow">&#x2192;</span>
          <div class="arch-box arch-box--pink">16 Tokens + 8 Gates<br><span style="font-size:0.7rem;opacity:0.7">[B, 16, 128] float32</span></div>
          <span class="arch-arrow">&#x2192;</span>
          <div class="arch-box arch-box--green">模型输入<br><span style="font-size:0.7rem;opacity:0.7">ChannelMAE ready</span></div>
        </div>

        <!-- Token table -->
        <div class="data-table-wrap">
          <table>
            <thead>
              <tr>
                <th>#</th><th>Token 名称</th><th>形状</th><th>类型</th><th>来源</th><th>物理含义</th>
              </tr>
            </thead>
            <tbody>
              <tr><td><span class="tag tag--purple">0</span></td><td><code>pdp_crop</code></td><td>[1, 64]</td><td>float32</td><td>IFFT(H)</td><td>功率延迟谱 — 多径时延分布</td></tr>
              <tr><td><span class="tag">1-4</span></td><td><code>srs_1 ~ srs_4</code></td><td>[1, 64]</td><td>complex64</td><td>SVD U 向量</td><td>空间特征 — 上行最优波束方向</td></tr>
              <tr><td><span class="tag tag--green">5-8</span></td><td><code>pmi_1 ~ pmi_4</code></td><td>[1, 64]</td><td>complex64</td><td>SVD V<sup>H</sup> 向量</td><td>预编码 — 下行波束赋形权重</td></tr>
              <tr><td><span class="tag tag--cyan">9-12</span></td><td><code>dft_1 ~ dft_4</code></td><td>[1, 64]</td><td>complex64</td><td>DFT 波束</td><td>角域能量 — Top-4 波束响应</td></tr>
              <tr><td><span class="tag tag--amber">13-14</span></td><td><code>rsrp_srs, rsrp_cb</code></td><td>[1, 64]</td><td>float32</td><td>功率测量</td><td>参考信号功率 (SRS / 码本)</td></tr>
              <tr><td><span class="tag tag--pink">15</span></td><td><code>cell_rsrp</code></td><td>[1, 16]</td><td>float32</td><td>SSB 测量</td><td>邻小区功率指纹</td></tr>
            </tbody>
          </table>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- STEP 3 & 4: Model & Eval -->
  <div class="two-col reveal mt-32">
    <div>
      <h3 style="color:#f1f5f9; font-size:1.1rem; margin-bottom:16px;">
        <span class="tag tag--green">Step 3</span> &nbsp;模型管理与排行榜
      </h3>
      <div class="card">
        <p style="color:#94a3b8; font-size:0.88rem; margin-bottom:16px;">
          上传 <code>.pt</code> 模型文件后，平台自动检查兼容性（token_dim, seq_len, latent_dim），
          通过则加入模型仓库。排行榜按 KNN 一致性降序排列，顶部显示金/银/铜奖牌。
        </p>
        <div class="data-table-wrap">
          <table>
            <thead><tr><th>排名</th><th>Run ID</th><th>KNN Acc</th><th>NMSE (dB)</th><th>CT</th><th>TW</th></tr></thead>
            <tbody>
              <tr><td><span style="color:#fbbf24;font-weight:700">&#x1F947; 1</span></td><td><code>run_2025a</code></td><td>87.3%</td><td>-18.4</td><td>0.921</td><td>0.895</td></tr>
              <tr><td><span style="color:#c0c0c0;font-weight:700">&#x1F948; 2</span></td><td><code>run_2024f</code></td><td>82.1%</td><td>-15.7</td><td>0.887</td><td>0.861</td></tr>
              <tr><td><span style="color:#cd7f32;font-weight:700">&#x1F949; 3</span></td><td><code>run_2024e</code></td><td>79.8%</td><td>-14.2</td><td>0.854</td><td>0.832</td></tr>
            </tbody>
          </table>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div>
      <h3 style="color:#f1f5f9; font-size:1.1rem; margin-bottom:16px;">
        <span class="tag tag--amber">Step 4</span> &nbsp;信道浏览与分析
      </h3>
      <div class="card">
        <p style="color:#94a3b8; font-size:0.88rem; margin-bottom:16px;">
          信道浏览器（ChannelExplorer）展示每个样本的理想信道、估计信道和误差热力图。
          蓝→白→红渐变直观呈现信道矩阵幅度分布，配合 Plotly 交互式特征图展示 16 个 Token 的提取结果。
        </p>
        <!-- Mini heatmap visualization -->
        <svg viewBox="0 0 380 120" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
          <!-- H_ideal -->
          <text x="60" y="14" text-anchor="middle" fill="#94a3b8" font-size="9">|H<tspan baseline-shift="sub" font-size="7">ideal</tspan>|</text>
          <rect x="10" y="20" width="100" height="80" rx="4" fill="none" stroke="rgba(255,255,255,0.08)" stroke-width="1"/>
          <rect x="12" y="22" width="12" height="10" rx="1" fill="#1a3a8a"/><rect x="26" y="22" width="12" height="10" rx="1" fill="#3060c0"/>
          <rect x="40" y="22" width="12" height="10" rx="1" fill="#6090e0"/><rect x="54" y="22" width="12" height="10" rx="1" fill="#a0b8f0"/>
          <rect x="68" y="22" width="12" height="10" rx="1" fill="#ffffff"/><rect x="82" y="22" width="12" height="10" rx="1" fill="#f0a0a0"/>
          <rect x="96" y="22" width="12" height="10" rx="1" fill="#d04040"/>
          <rect x="12" y="34" width="12" height="10" rx="1" fill="#4070d0"/><rect x="26" y="34" width="12" height="10" rx="1" fill="#ffffff"/>
          <rect x="40" y="34" width="12" height="10" rx="1" fill="#e08080"/><rect x="54" y="34" width="12" height="10" rx="1" fill="#c04040"/>
          <rect x="68" y="34" width="12" height="10" rx="1" fill="#8030a0"/><rect x="82" y="34" width="12" height="10" rx="1" fill="#4070d0"/>
          <rect x="96" y="34" width="12" height="10" rx="1" fill="#2050b0"/>
          <rect x="12" y="46" width="12" height="10" rx="1" fill="#d06060"/><rect x="26" y="46" width="12" height="10" rx="1" fill="#a04040"/>
          <rect x="40" y="46" width="12" height="10" rx="1" fill="#3060c0"/><rect x="54" y="46" width="12" height="10" rx="1" fill="#1a3a8a"/>
          <rect x="68" y="46" width="12" height="10" rx="1" fill="#6090e0"/><rect x="82" y="46" width="12" height="10" rx="1" fill="#ffffff"/>
          <rect x="96" y="46" width="12" height="10" rx="1" fill="#c04040"/>

          <!-- H_est -->
          <text x="200" y="14" text-anchor="middle" fill="#94a3b8" font-size="9">|H<tspan baseline-shift="sub" font-size="7">est</tspan>|</text>
          <rect x="145" y="20" width="100" height="80" rx="4" fill="none" stroke="rgba(255,255,255,0.08)" stroke-width="1"/>
          <rect x="147" y="22" width="12" height="10" rx="1" fill="#1a3a8a"/><rect x="161" y="22" width="12" height="10" rx="1" fill="#3060c0"/>
          <rect x="175" y="22" width="12" height="10" rx="1" fill="#5580d8"/><rect x="189" y="22" width="12" height="10" rx="1" fill="#a0b8f0"/>
          <rect x="203" y="22" width="12" height="10" rx="1" fill="#f0e8e8"/><rect x="217" y="22" width="12" height="10" rx="1" fill="#e89898"/>
          <rect x="231" y="22" width="12" height="10" rx="1" fill="#c83838"/>

          <!-- Error -->
          <text x="330" y="14" text-anchor="middle" fill="#94a3b8" font-size="9">|Error|</text>
          <rect x="280" y="20" width="100" height="80" rx="4" fill="none" stroke="rgba(255,255,255,0.08)" stroke-width="1"/>
          <rect x="282" y="22" width="12" height="10" rx="1" fill="#1a2a40"/><rect x="296" y="22" width="12" height="10" rx="1" fill="#1a2a40"/>
          <rect x="310" y="22" width="12" height="10" rx="1" fill="#203050"/><rect x="324" y="22" width="12" height="10" rx="1" fill="#1a2a40"/>
          <rect x="338" y="22" width="12" height="10" rx="1" fill="#2a4060"/><rect x="352" y="22" width="12" height="10" rx="1" fill="#203050"/>
          <rect x="366" y="22" width="12" height="10" rx="1" fill="#1a2a40"/>

          <!-- Color bar -->
          <defs><linearGradient id="heatGrad" x1="0" y1="0" x2="1" y2="0"><stop offset="0%" stop-color="#1a3a8a"/><stop offset="50%" stop-color="#ffffff"/><stop offset="100%" stop-color="#d04040"/></linearGradient></defs>
          <rect x="120" y="108" width="140" height="6" rx="3" fill="url(#heatGrad)"/>
