      <text x="350" y="240" text-anchor="middle" fill="#d97706" font-size="7">码本 SINR</text>

      <rect x="420" y="185" width="100" height="70" rx="8" fill="rgba(245,158,11,0.08)" stroke="rgba(245,158,11,0.2)" stroke-width="1"/>
      <text x="470" y="205" text-anchor="middle" fill="#fcd34d" font-size="9" font-weight="600">G7</text>
      <text x="470" y="222" text-anchor="middle" fill="#fbbf24" font-size="8">cqi</text>
      <text x="470" y="240" text-anchor="middle" fill="#d97706" font-size="7">CQI (0~15)</text>

      <!-- Gate mechanism -->
      <rect x="580" y="185" width="380" height="70" rx="8" fill="rgba(139,92,246,0.08)" stroke="rgba(139,92,246,0.2)" stroke-width="1"/>
      <text x="770" y="205" text-anchor="middle" fill="#c4b5fd" font-size="10" font-weight="600">门控机制</text>
      <text x="770" y="228" text-anchor="middle" fill="#a78bfa" font-size="11" font-family="Cambria Math, serif">gate = sigmoid(x) × 0.3 + 0.7</text>
      <text x="770" y="248" text-anchor="middle" fill="#7c3aed" font-size="9">输出范围 [0.7, 1.0] — 软抑制低质量特征，永不完全屏蔽</text>

      <!-- Connection arrows -->
      <text x="500" y="290" text-anchor="middle" fill="#64748b" font-size="9">Gates 对 Token 进行逐元素加权：token_gated = token × gate</text>
      <text x="500" y="310" text-anchor="middle" fill="#64748b" font-size="9">低 SINR → gate ≈ 0.7 (抑制噪声)&nbsp;&nbsp;|&nbsp;&nbsp;高 SINR → gate ≈ 1.0 (完全信任)</text>

      <!-- Summary -->
      <rect x="200" y="330" width="600" height="40" rx="10" fill="rgba(59,130,246,0.08)" stroke="rgba(59,130,246,0.15)" stroke-width="1"/>
      <text x="500" y="355" text-anchor="middle" fill="#93c5fd" font-size="11" font-weight="600">最终模型输入: [Batch, 16, 128] float32 — 统一维度，跨源可比</text>
    </svg>
    <div class="svg-title">16 Token + 8 Gate 完整架构：每个 Token 对应明确的物理测量量，Gate 机制保证特征质量自适应</div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ========================= 7. TECH DEEP DIVES ========================= -->
<section id="tech-deep">
  <div class="reveal">
    <div class="section-label">Technical Deep Dives</div>
    <h2 class="section-title">核心技术图解</h2>
    <p class="section-desc">从 SRS 频率跳频到多小区干扰建模，从路损公式到信道估计 —— 深入代码级的技术细节。</p>
  </div>

  <!-- 7a: SRS Hopping -->
  <div class="reveal mt-16">
    <h3 style="color:#f1f5f9; font-size:1.1rem; margin-bottom:4px;">SRS 频率跳频 (3GPP 38.211 §6.4.1.4.3)</h3>
    <p class="text-sm text-muted mb-16">通过带宽树分层跳频，SRS 在少量 Symbol 内覆盖全带宽，是信道探测的核心机制。</p>
  </div>

  <div class="two-col">
    <div class="svg-container reveal reveal-delay-1">
      <svg viewBox="0 0 440 320" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
        <!-- Bandwidth tree -->
        <!-- Level 0 (root) -->
        <rect x="120" y="10" width="200" height="32" rx="6" fill="rgba(59,130,246,0.15)" stroke="rgba(59,130,246,0.4)" stroke-width="1.5"/>
        <text x="220" y="30" text-anchor="middle" fill="#93c5fd" font-size="10" font-weight="600">B_SRS=0 (全带宽) m₀=272 RB</text>

        <!-- Level 1 -->
        <line x1="170" y1="42" x2="110" y2="70" stroke="#475569" stroke-width="1"/>
        <line x1="270" y1="42" x2="330" y2="70" stroke="#475569" stroke-width="1"/>
        <rect x="40" y="70" width="140" height="28" rx="6" fill="rgba(139,92,246,0.12)" stroke="rgba(139,92,246,0.3)" stroke-width="1"/>
        <text x="110" y="88" text-anchor="middle" fill="#c4b5fd" font-size="9">B_SRS=1 · m₁=136 · N₁=2</text>
        <rect x="260" y="70" width="140" height="28" rx="6" fill="rgba(139,92,246,0.12)" stroke="rgba(139,92,246,0.3)" stroke-width="1"/>
        <text x="330" y="88" text-anchor="middle" fill="#c4b5fd" font-size="9">B_SRS=1 · m₁=136 · N₁=2</text>

        <!-- Level 2 -->
        <line x1="80" y1="98" x2="55" y2="126" stroke="#475569" stroke-width="1"/>
        <line x1="140" y1="98" x2="165" y2="126" stroke="#475569" stroke-width="1"/>
        <line x1="300" y1="98" x2="275" y2="126" stroke="#475569" stroke-width="1"/>
        <line x1="360" y1="98" x2="385" y2="126" stroke="#475569" stroke-width="1"/>
        <rect x="10" y="126" width="90" height="24" rx="5" fill="rgba(6,182,212,0.12)" stroke="rgba(6,182,212,0.3)" stroke-width="1"/>
        <text x="55" y="142" text-anchor="middle" fill="#67e8f9" font-size="8">B₂=2 · m₂=68</text>
        <rect x="120" y="126" width="90" height="24" rx="5" fill="rgba(6,182,212,0.12)" stroke="rgba(6,182,212,0.3)" stroke-width="1"/>
        <text x="165" y="142" text-anchor="middle" fill="#67e8f9" font-size="8">B₂=2 · m₂=68</text>
        <rect x="230" y="126" width="90" height="24" rx="5" fill="rgba(6,182,212,0.12)" stroke="rgba(6,182,212,0.3)" stroke-width="1"/>
        <text x="275" y="142" text-anchor="middle" fill="#67e8f9" font-size="8">B₂=2 · m₂=68</text>
        <rect x="340" y="126" width="90" height="24" rx="5" fill="rgba(6,182,212,0.12)" stroke="rgba(6,182,212,0.3)" stroke-width="1"/>
        <text x="385" y="142" text-anchor="middle" fill="#67e8f9" font-size="8">B₂=2 · m₂=68</text>

        <!-- Hopping pattern -->
        <text x="220" y="180" text-anchor="middle" fill="#94a3b8" font-size="10" font-weight="600">跳频序列示意 (4个时隙)</text>
        <!-- Frequency grid -->
        <rect x="30" y="195" width="90" height="24" rx="4" fill="rgba(59,130,246,0.3)" stroke="rgba(59,130,246,0.5)" stroke-width="1"/>
        <text x="75" y="211" text-anchor="middle" fill="#fff" font-size="8" font-weight="600">Slot 0</text>
        <rect x="30" y="195" width="90" height="24" rx="4" fill="rgba(59,130,246,0.25)"/>

        <rect x="140" y="219" width="90" height="24" rx="4" fill="rgba(139,92,246,0.3)" stroke="rgba(139,92,246,0.5)" stroke-width="1"/>
        <text x="185" y="235" text-anchor="middle" fill="#fff" font-size="8" font-weight="600">Slot 1</text>

        <rect x="250" y="243" width="90" height="24" rx="4" fill="rgba(6,182,212,0.3)" stroke="rgba(6,182,212,0.5)" stroke-width="1"/>
        <text x="295" y="259" text-anchor="middle" fill="#fff" font-size="8" font-weight="600">Slot 2</text>

        <rect x="360" y="195" width="60" height="72" rx="4" fill="none" stroke="rgba(34,197,94,0.3)" stroke-width="1" stroke-dasharray="3,3"/>
        <rect x="360" y="267" width="60" height="24" rx="4" fill="rgba(34,197,94,0.3)" stroke="rgba(34,197,94,0.5)" stroke-width="1"/>
        <text x="390" y="283" text-anchor="middle" fill="#fff" font-size="8" font-weight="600">Slot 3</text>

        <!-- Axis labels -->
        <text x="15" y="255" text-anchor="end" fill="#64748b" font-size="8" transform="rotate(-90,15,255)">频率 &#x2191;</text>
        <text x="220" y="305" text-anchor="middle" fill="#64748b" font-size="8">时间 &#x2192;</text>
        <text x="220" y="318" text-anchor="middle" fill="#475569" font-size="7">cycle_length = N₁ × N₂ = 2 × 2 = 4 slots 覆盖全带宽</text>
      </svg>
      <div class="svg-title">SRS 带宽树分层跳频 — 4时隙完成全带宽探测</div>
    </div>

    <div class="reveal reveal-delay-2">
      <div class="formula-block">
        <span class="formula-label">SRS 频率起始位置</span>
        <span class="formula">
          <var class="var">k</var><sub>0</sub><sup>(p<sub>i</sub>)</sup> = <var class="var">k</var><sub>0,bar</sub> +
          &Sigma;<sub><var class="var">b</var>=0</sub><sup><var class="var">B</var><sub>SRS</sub></sup>
          <var class="var">K</var><sub>TC</sub> &middot; <var class="var">m</var><sub>SRS,b</sub> &middot; <var class="var">n</var><sub>b</sub>
        </span>
      </div>
      <div class="formula-block">
        <span class="formula-label">跳频索引 (b > b_hop)</span>
        <span class="formula">
          <var class="var">F</var><sub>b</sub>(<var class="var">n</var><sub>SRS</sub>) =
          (<var class="var">n</var><sub>SRS</sub> / &Pi;<sub>b'=b<sub>hop</sub>+1</sub><sup>b-1</sup> <var class="var">N</var><sub>b'</sub>)
          mod <var class="var">N</var><sub>b</sub>
        </span>
      </div>
      <div class="formula-block">
        <span class="formula-label">跳频周期</span>
        <span class="formula">
          Cycle = &Pi;<sub><var class="var">b</var>=b<sub>hop</sub>+1</sub><sup><var class="var">B</var><sub>SRS</sub></sup>
          <var class="var">N</var><sub>b</sub>
        </span>
      </div>
      <p class="text-sm text-muted mt-16">
        平台完整实现了 3GPP TS 38.211 的 SRS 序列生成（Zadoff-Chu 基序列 + 循环移位）和频率跳频树结构。
        <code>K_TC</code> 为梳齿因子（2/4/8），<code>B_SRS</code> 为带宽配置级数（0~3），
        跳频通过 <code>F_b</code> 在每个时隙自动轮转频率位置。
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="divider"></div>

  <!-- 7b: Interference Modeling -->
  <div class="reveal">
    <h3 style="color:#f1f5f9; font-size:1.1rem; margin-bottom:4px;">物理级干扰建模</h3>
    <p class="text-sm text-muted mb-16">不是简单加高斯噪声等效 — 平台建模每个邻小区的独立信道、导频序列叠加和接收信号处理。</p>
  </div>

  <div class="two-col">
    <div class="svg-container reveal reveal-delay-1">
      <svg viewBox="0 0 440 350" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
        <!-- Serving cell -->
        <circle cx="220" cy="170" r="60" fill="none" stroke="rgba(59,130,246,0.2)" stroke-width="1" stroke-dasharray="4,4"/>
        <circle cx="220" cy="170" r="14" fill="#fff" stroke="#3b82f6" stroke-width="3"/>
        <text x="220" y="175" text-anchor="middle" fill="#3b82f6" font-size="10" font-weight="700">S</text>
        <text x="220" y="195" text-anchor="middle" fill="#93c5fd" font-size="8">服务小区</text>

        <!-- UE -->
        <circle cx="260" cy="200" r="8" fill="#3b82f6" opacity="0.8"/>
        <text x="260" y="204" text-anchor="middle" fill="#fff" font-size="7" font-weight="600">UE</text>

        <!-- Serving signal -->
        <line x1="232" y1="178" x2="253" y2="196" stroke="#3b82f6" stroke-width="2"/>
        <text x="235" y="180" fill="#60a5fa" font-size="7">h<tspan baseline-shift="sub" font-size="5">serv</tspan></text>

        <!-- Interferer 1 -->
        <circle cx="80" cy="80" r="12" fill="#fff" stroke="#f97316" stroke-width="2.5"/>
        <text x="80" y="84" text-anchor="middle" fill="#f97316" font-size="9" font-weight="700">I₁</text>
        <line x1="90" y1="88" x2="252" y2="196" stroke="#f97316" stroke-width="1" stroke-dasharray="4,3" opacity="0.6"/>
        <text x="150" y="130" fill="#fbbf24" font-size="7" transform="rotate(-30,150,130)">h<tspan baseline-shift="sub" font-size="5">intf,1</tspan></text>

        <!-- Interferer 2 -->
        <circle cx="370" cy="70" r="12" fill="#fff" stroke="#22c55e" stroke-width="2.5"/>
        <text x="370" y="74" text-anchor="middle" fill="#22c55e" font-size="9" font-weight="700">I₂</text>
        <line x1="362" y1="80" x2="268" y2="196" stroke="#22c55e" stroke-width="1" stroke-dasharray="4,3" opacity="0.6"/>
        <text x="325" y="125" fill="#4ade80" font-size="7" transform="rotate(25,325,125)">h<tspan baseline-shift="sub" font-size="5">intf,2</tspan></text>

        <!-- Interferer 3 -->
        <circle cx="100" cy="290" r="12" fill="#fff" stroke="#a855f7" stroke-width="2.5"/>
        <text x="100" y="294" text-anchor="middle" fill="#a855f7" font-size="9" font-weight="700">I₃</text>
        <line x1="110" y1="284" x2="254" y2="206" stroke="#a855f7" stroke-width="1" stroke-dasharray="4,3" opacity="0.6"/>

        <!-- UL label -->
        <rect x="290" y="155" width="140" height="50" rx="8" fill="rgba(15,23,42,0.7)" stroke="rgba(255,255,255,0.06)" stroke-width="1"/>
        <text x="360" y="172" text-anchor="middle" fill="#fbbf24" font-size="8" font-weight="600">UL: 多 UE SRS 叠加</text>
        <text x="360" y="186" text-anchor="middle" fill="#64748b" font-size="7">每邻区随机 [0, K] 个 UE</text>
        <text x="360" y="198" text-anchor="middle" fill="#64748b" font-size="7">Zadoff-Chu 序列正交</text>

        <!-- DL label -->
        <rect x="290" y="220" width="140" height="50" rx="8" fill="rgba(15,23,42,0.7)" stroke="rgba(255,255,255,0.06)" stroke-width="1"/>
        <text x="360" y="237" text-anchor="middle" fill="#4ade80" font-size="8" font-weight="600">DL: 多小区 CSI-RS 叠加</text>
        <text x="360" y="251" text-anchor="middle" fill="#64748b" font-size="7">随机子集 [0, K-1] 小区</text>
        <text x="360" y="263" text-anchor="middle" fill="#64748b" font-size="7">Gold-PRBS 序列</text>

        <!-- Noise -->
        <text x="220" y="330" text-anchor="middle" fill="#f87171" font-size="8">+ AWGN (per-RB bandwidth)</text>
      </svg>
      <div class="svg-title">多小区干扰模型 — 每个邻区建模独立信道+导频叠加</div>
    </div>

    <div class="reveal reveal-delay-2">
      <div class="formula-block">
        <span class="formula-label">UL 接收信号 (BS 端)</span>
        <span class="formula">
          <var class="var">Y</var> = <var class="var">h</var><sub>serv</sub> &middot; <var class="var">x</var><sub>SRS,serv</sub>
          + &Sigma;<sub>k</sub> <var class="var">h</var><sub>intf,k</sub> &middot; <var class="var">x</var><sub>SRS,k</sub>
          + <var class="var">n</var>
        </span>
      </div>
      <div class="formula-block">
        <span class="formula-label">SIR 计算</span>
        <span class="formula">
          SIR<sub>dB</sub> = 10 &middot; log<sub>10</sub>
          (<var class="var">P</var><sub>serv</sub> / <var class="var">P</var><sub>intf</sub>),&nbsp;
          clamped to [-50, 50] dB
        </span>
      </div>
      <div class="formula-block">
        <span class="formula-label">SINR (线性域)</span>
        <span class="formula">
          SINR = <var class="var">P</var><sub>serv</sub> /
          (<var class="var">P</var><sub>intf</sub> + 2 &middot; <var class="var">P</var><sub>noise</sub>)
        </span>
      </div>
      <div class="formula-block">
        <span class="formula-label">噪声功率 (per-RB)</span>
        <span class="formula">
          <var class="var">P</var><sub>noise</sub> = <var class="var">kT</var> &middot; (12 &middot; SCS) + NF
          <br><span style="font-size:0.8em;color:#f87171">&#x26A0; 非系统总带宽！F-003 修复关键点</span>
        </span>
      </div>
      <p class="text-sm text-muted mt-16">
        干扰建模的核心在于：每个邻小区有独立的物理信道 <code>h_intf,k</code>，干扰信号经过各自信道后在接收端叠加。
        这比简单的 "SINR = SNR - X dB" 模型更接近真实系统，能产生有意义的空间干扰梯度。
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="divider"></div>

  <!-- 7c: Channel Estimation -->
  <div class="reveal">
    <h3 style="color:#f1f5f9; font-size:1.1rem; margin-bottom:4px;">信道估计：LS vs MMSE</h3>
    <p class="text-sm text-muted mb-16">平台同时支持最小二乘(LS)和最小均方误差(MMSE)两种信道估计模式，以及理想信道直通。</p>
  </div>

  <div class="two-col reveal">
    <div>
      <div class="formula-block">
        <span class="formula-label">LS 信道估计 (Least Squares)</span>
        <span class="formula">
          <var class="var">H&#770;</var><sub>LS</sub>[k,r] =
          (<var class="var">Y</var><sub>RS</sub>[k,r] &middot; <var class="var">X</var><sub>RS</sub><sup>*</sup>[k])
          / (|<var class="var">X</var><sub>RS</sub>[k]|<sup>2</sup> + &epsilon;)
        </span>
      </div>
      <p class="text-sm text-muted mt-8">
        最简单的估计方式，直接用接收信号除以已知导频。无需信道统计先验，但噪声放大严重。
        正则化常数 &epsilon; = 10<sup>-12</sup> 防止除零。
      </p>
    </div>
    <div>
      <div class="formula-block">
        <span class="formula-label">MMSE 信道估计 (Wiener 滤波)</span>
        <span class="formula">
          <var class="var">H&#770;</var><sub>MMSE</sub> = <var class="var">R</var><sub>hh</sub> &middot;
          (<var class="var">R</var><sub>hh</sub> + SNR<sup>-1</sup> &middot; <var class="var">I</var>)<sup>-1</sup>
          &middot; <var class="var">H&#770;</var><sub>LS</sub>
        </span>
      </div>
      <div class="formula-block mt-8">
        <span class="formula-label">频域相关 (指数 PDP)</span>
        <span class="formula">
          <var class="var">R</var>[k,l] = 1 / (1 + j&middot;2&pi;&middot;(k-l)&middot;&Delta;f&middot;&tau;<sub>rms</sub>)
        </span>
      </div>
      <p class="text-sm text-muted mt-8">
        利用信道的频域相关性进行降噪滤波。空间协方差通过 IIR 时域平滑（&alpha;=0.2）估计。
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="divider"></div>

  <!-- 7d: Path Loss -->
  <div class="reveal">
    <h3 style="color:#f1f5f9; font-size:1.1rem; margin-bottom:4px;">路径损耗模型 (3GPP 38.901)</h3>
    <p class="text-sm text-muted mb-16">平台实现了完整的 3GPP 38.901 Table 7.4.1-1 路损模型，覆盖 UMa/UMi/InF 三大场景。</p>
  </div>

  <div class="card-grid card-grid--3 reveal">
    <div class="card">
      <h3 style="color:#93c5fd; font-size:0.95rem;">UMa NLOS</h3>
      <div class="formula-block" style="padding:14px 18px;">
        <span class="formula" style="font-size:0.9em;">
          PL = <span class="const">13.54</span> + <span class="const">39.08</span>&middot;log<sub>10</sub>(<var class="var">d</var><sub>3d</sub>)
          + <span class="const">20</span>&middot;log<sub>10</sub>(<var class="var">f</var><sub>c</sub>)
          - <span class="const">0.6</span>&middot;(<var class="var">h</var><sub>UT</sub> - 1.5)
        </span>
      </div>
      <p class="text-xs text-muted">&sigma;<sub>SF</sub> = 6 dB</p>
    </div>
    <div class="card">
      <h3 style="color:#fcd34d; font-size:0.95rem;">UMi NLOS</h3>
      <div class="formula-block" style="padding:14px 18px;">
        <span class="formula" style="font-size:0.9em;">
          PL = <span class="const">22.4</span> + <span class="const">35.3</span>&middot;log<sub>10</sub>(<var class="var">d</var><sub>3d</sub>)
          + <span class="const">21.3</span>&middot;log<sub>10</sub>(<var class="var">f</var><sub>c</sub>)
          - <span class="const">0.3</span>&middot;(<var class="var">h</var><sub>UT</sub> - 1.5)
        </span>
      </div>
      <p class="text-xs text-muted">&sigma;<sub>SF</sub> = 7.82 dB</p>
    </div>
    <div class="card">
      <h3 style="color:#86efac; font-size:0.95rem;">InF-SH NLOS</h3>
      <div class="formula-block" style="padding:14px 18px;">
        <span class="formula" style="font-size:0.9em;">
          PL = <span class="const">31.84</span> + <span class="const">21.50</span>&middot;log<sub>10</sub>(<var class="var">d</var><sub>3d</sub>)
          + <span class="const">19</span>&middot;log<sub>10</sub>(<var class="var">f</var><sub>c</sub>)
        </span>
      </div>
      <p class="text-xs text-muted">&sigma;<sub>SF</sub> = 7.56 dB</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="reveal mt-24">
    <div class="formula-block">
      <span class="formula-label">LOS 概率 — UMa</span>
      <span class="formula">
        P<sub>LOS</sub>(<var class="var">d</var><sub>2D</sub>) =
        min(18/<var class="var">d</var><sub>2D</sub>, 1) &middot;
        (1 - e<sup>-<var class="var">d</var><sub>2D</sub>/63</sup>) +
        e<sup>-<var class="var">d</var><sub>2D</sub>/63</sup>
      </span>
    </div>
    <div class="formula-block">
      <span class="formula-label">LOS 断点距离</span>
      <span class="formula">
        <var class="var">d</var><sub>BP</sub> = 4 &middot; <var class="var">h</var><sub>BS,eff</sub> &middot;
        <var class="var">h</var><sub>UT,eff</sub> &middot; <var class="var">f</var><sub>c</sub> &middot; 10<sup>9</sup> / <var class="var">c</var>
        &nbsp;&nbsp;|&nbsp;&nbsp;<var class="var">c</var> = 3&times;10<sup>8</sup> m/s
      </span>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ========================= 8. CHANNEL MAE MODEL ========================= -->
<section id="model">
  <div class="reveal">
    <div class="section-label">Model Architecture</div>
    <h2 class="section-title">ChannelMAE 模型架构</h2>
    <p class="section-desc">Masked Autoencoder + 对比学习的双目标训练框架，输出 16 维 L2 归一化 Embedding。</p>
  </div>

  <!-- Model architecture SVG -->
  <div class="svg-container reveal reveal-delay-1">
    <svg viewBox="0 0 960 300" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
      <!-- Input -->
      <rect x="10" y="100" width="100" height="60" rx="10" fill="rgba(244,114,182,0.15)" stroke="rgba(244,114,182,0.4)" stroke-width="1.5"/>
      <text x="60" y="125" text-anchor="middle" fill="#f9a8d4" font-size="10" font-weight="600">模型输入</text>
      <text x="60" y="142" text-anchor="middle" fill="#db2777" font-size="8">[B, 16, 128]</text>

      <!-- Arrow -->
      <line x1="110" y1="130" x2="145" y2="130" stroke="#475569" stroke-width="1.5" marker-end="url(#arrowhead)"/>

      <!-- Transformer Encoder -->
      <rect x="150" y="70" width="160" height="120" rx="12" fill="rgba(59,130,246,0.12)" stroke="rgba(59,130,246,0.4)" stroke-width="2"/>
      <text x="230" y="98" text-anchor="middle" fill="#93c5fd" font-size="11" font-weight="700">Transformer Encoder</text>
      <text x="230" y="118" text-anchor="middle" fill="#60a5fa" font-size="9">4 layers · 8 heads</text>
      <text x="230" y="136" text-anchor="middle" fill="#60a5fa" font-size="9">dim=128 · FFN=512</text>
      <text x="230" y="154" text-anchor="middle" fill="#3b82f6" font-size="8">Pre-LN · GELU · Dropout</text>
      <text x="230" y="172" text-anchor="middle" fill="#3b82f6" font-size="8">+ Learnable Pos Embedding</text>

      <!-- Arrow -->
      <line x1="310" y1="130" x2="345" y2="130" stroke="#475569" stroke-width="1.5" marker-end="url(#arrowhead)"/>

      <!-- MLP Bottleneck -->
      <rect x="350" y="90" width="100" height="80" rx="10" fill="rgba(139,92,246,0.15)" stroke="rgba(139,92,246,0.4)" stroke-width="1.5"/>
      <text x="400" y="118" text-anchor="middle" fill="#c4b5fd" font-size="10" font-weight="600">MLP</text>
      <text x="400" y="136" text-anchor="middle" fill="#a78bfa" font-size="9">128→256→128</text>
      <text x="400" y="152" text-anchor="middle" fill="#7c3aed" font-size="8">Bottleneck</text>

      <!-- Arrow -->
      <line x1="450" y1="130" x2="485" y2="130" stroke="#475569" stroke-width="1.5" marker-end="url(#arrowhead)"/>

      <!-- Energy-weighted Pooling -->
      <rect x="490" y="85" width="120" height="90" rx="10" fill="rgba(6,182,212,0.15)" stroke="rgba(6,182,212,0.4)" stroke-width="1.5"/>
      <text x="550" y="112" text-anchor="middle" fill="#67e8f9" font-size="10" font-weight="600">能量加权池化</text>
      <text x="550" y="130" text-anchor="middle" fill="#22d3ee" font-size="8">w = softmax(||mlp||)</text>
      <text x="550" y="146" text-anchor="middle" fill="#0891b2" font-size="8">z = &Sigma; w<tspan baseline-shift="sub" font-size="6">i</tspan> &middot; x<tspan baseline-shift="sub" font-size="6">i</tspan></text>
      <text x="550" y="162" text-anchor="middle" fill="#0891b2" font-size="7">[B, 128] → [B, 128]</text>

      <!-- Arrow -->
      <line x1="610" y1="130" x2="645" y2="130" stroke="#475569" stroke-width="1.5" marker-end="url(#arrowhead)"/>

      <!-- Latent Projection -->
      <rect x="650" y="85" width="120" height="90" rx="10" fill="rgba(34,197,94,0.15)" stroke="rgba(34,197,94,0.4)" stroke-width="1.5"/>
      <text x="710" y="108" text-anchor="middle" fill="#86efac" font-size="10" font-weight="600">Latent Proj</text>
      <text x="710" y="126" text-anchor="middle" fill="#4ade80" font-size="8">LN → 128→64</text>
      <text x="710" y="142" text-anchor="middle" fill="#4ade80" font-size="8">GELU → 64→16</text>
      <text x="710" y="158" text-anchor="middle" fill="#16a34a" font-size="8">+ Shortcut(128→16)</text>

      <!-- Arrow -->
      <line x1="770" y1="130" x2="805" y2="130" stroke="#475569" stroke-width="1.5" marker-end="url(#arrowhead)"/>

      <!-- L2 Norm -->
      <rect x="810" y="95" width="100" height="70" rx="10" fill="rgba(245,158,11,0.15)" stroke="rgba(245,158,11,0.4)" stroke-width="2"/>
      <text x="860" y="120" text-anchor="middle" fill="#fcd34d" font-size="11" font-weight="700">16-D</text>
      <text x="860" y="138" text-anchor="middle" fill="#fbbf24" font-size="9">Embedding</text>
      <text x="860" y="154" text-anchor="middle" fill="#d97706" font-size="8">L2 归一化</text>

      <!-- Decoder branch (below) -->
      <line x1="400" y1="170" x2="400" y2="220" stroke="#475569" stroke-width="1" stroke-dasharray="4,3"/>
      <rect x="330" y="225" width="140" height="60" rx="10" fill="rgba(239,68,68,0.1)" stroke="rgba(239,68,68,0.25)" stroke-width="1" stroke-dasharray="3,3"/>
      <text x="400" y="248" text-anchor="middle" fill="#f87171" font-size="9" font-weight="600">Transformer Decoder</text>
      <text x="400" y="265" text-anchor="middle" fill="#ef4444" font-size="8">2 layers · 重构损失</text>
      <text x="400" y="278" text-anchor="middle" fill="#dc2626" font-size="7">仅训练时使用</text>

      <!-- Contrastive branch (above) -->
      <line x1="860" y1="95" x2="860" y2="50" stroke="#475569" stroke-width="1" stroke-dasharray="4,3"/>
      <rect x="790" y="10" width="140" height="36" rx="8" fill="rgba(59,130,246,0.1)" stroke="rgba(59,130,246,0.2)" stroke-width="1" stroke-dasharray="3,3"/>
      <text x="860" y="33" text-anchor="middle" fill="#60a5fa" font-size="9" font-weight="600">InfoNCE 对比损失</text>

      <defs>
        <marker id="arrowhead" markerWidth="8" markerHeight="6" refX="8" refY="3" orient="auto">
          <polygon points="0 0, 8 3, 0 6" fill="#60a5fa"/>
        </marker>
      </defs>
    </svg>
    <div class="svg-title">ChannelMAE: Encoder(4L) → MLP → 能量加权池化 → Latent(128→16) → L2 Embedding</div>
  </div>

  <!-- Loss functions -->
  <div class="two-col reveal mt-24">
    <div>
      <div class="formula-block">
        <span class="formula-label">重构损失 (加权 MSE)</span>
        <span class="formula">
          L<sub>recon</sub> = &Sigma;<sub>slot</sub> <var class="var">w</var><sub>slot</sub> &middot;
          MSE(<var class="var">recon</var>, <var class="var">target</var> | <var class="var">active</var>)
        </span>
      </div>
      <p class="text-sm text-muted mt-8">
        不同 Token 权重不同：SRS(&times;2.0) > PMI(&times;1.5) > PDP/DFT/RSRP(&times;1.0) > Cell RSRP(&times;0.5)。
        空间特征（SRS/PMI）获得更高权重，因为它们对信道表征最关键。
      </p>
    </div>
    <div>
      <div class="formula-block">
        <span class="formula-label">对比损失 (Symmetric InfoNCE)</span>
        <span class="formula">
          L<sub>cont</sub> = [CE(z<sub>1</sub>&middot;z<sub>2</sub><sup>T</sup>/&tau;, labels) +
          CE(z<sub>2</sub>&middot;z<sub>1</sub><sup>T</sup>/&tau;, labels)] / 2
        </span>
      </div>
      <p class="text-sm text-muted mt-8">
        配对样本（同一位置 UL/DL 或相邻时刻）作为正样本对，温度参数 &tau; 控制分布锐度。
        额外正则项：正交损失 + 时间平滑 + 均匀分布约束。
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ========================= 9. EVALUATION ========================= -->
<section id="eval">
  <div class="reveal">
    <div class="section-label">Evaluation Framework</div>
    <h2 class="section-title">6 维标准化评估体系</h2>
    <p class="section-desc">基于 Channel Charting 理论的全方位评估框架，测试集锁定 + 版本化，结果可复现。</p>
  </div>

  <div class="metric-grid reveal">
    <div class="metric-card">
      <div class="metric-name">Continuity (CT)</div>
      <div class="metric-formula">rank(D<sub>emb</sub>) vs rank(D<sub>phy</sub>)</div>
      <div class="metric-desc">嵌入空间近邻在物理空间也近邻的比例 — 衡量局部结构保持</div>
    </div>
    <div class="metric-card">
      <div class="metric-name">Trustworthiness (TW)</div>
      <div class="metric-formula">Lee &amp; Verleysen (2009)</div>
      <div class="metric-desc">物理空间近邻在嵌入空间也近邻的比例 — CT 的对称指标</div>
    </div>
    <div class="metric-card">
      <div class="metric-name">KNN Consistency</div>
      <div class="metric-formula">&Sigma; sim(attr<sub>i</sub>, attr<sub>NN(i)</sub>) / K</div>
      <div class="metric-desc">K近邻的物理属性（SNR/SIR/移动模式）一致性</div>
    </div>
    <div class="metric-card">
      <div class="metric-name">NMSE (dB)</div>
      <div class="metric-formula">10&middot;log<sub>10</sub>(||H-H&#770;||<sup>2</sup>/||H||<sup>2</sup>)</div>
      <div class="metric-desc">归一化均方误差 — 重构质量的直接度量</div>
    </div>
    <div class="metric-card">
      <div class="metric-name">Cosine Separation</div>
      <div class="metric-formula">margin(cos<sub>pos</sub> - cos<sub>neg</sub>)</div>
      <div class="metric-desc">正样本对与负样本对的余弦相似度分离度</div>
    </div>
    <div class="metric-card">
      <div class="metric-name">Kendall &tau;</div>
      <div class="metric-formula">(concordant - discordant) / C(n,2)</div>
      <div class="metric-desc">嵌入距离与物理距离的全局秩相关系数</div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="card reveal mt-32">
    <h3>评估流程保障</h3>
    <div class="two-col mt-16">
      <div>
        <p class="text-sm" style="color:#94a3b8;">
          <span class="highlight">测试集锁定</span>：评估使用固定划分的测试集，不随训练数据变动。
          数据集版本化管理，确保不同模型在完全相同的数据上比较。
        </p>
      </div>
      <div>
        <p class="text-sm" style="color:#94a3b8;">
          <span class="highlight">自动化流水线</span>：<code>run_eval()</code> 一键完成 checkpoint 加载 → embedding 收集 →
          6 指标计算 → 结果持久化 → 排行榜更新。支持 UMAP/t-SNE 2D 降维可视化。
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ========================= 10. ENGINEERING CHALLENGES ========================= -->
<section id="challenges">
  <div class="reveal">
    <div class="section-label">Engineering Challenges</div>
    <h2 class="section-title">工程挑战与巧思</h2>
    <p class="section-desc">从 Git 历史中提炼的 8 个真实技术难题 —— 每一个都是在生产级代码中发现并解决的非显然问题。</p>
  </div>

  <!-- Challenge 1 -->
  <div class="challenge-card reveal">
    <div class="challenge-header">
      <span class="challenge-id">F-003</span>
      <span class="challenge-title">噪声带宽计算错误 — 虚高 24.4 dB</span>
    </div>
    <div class="challenge-section">
      <div class="challenge-section-label problem">&#x1F534; 问题</div>
      <p>三个数据源全部使用系统总带宽（N_RB &times; 12 &times; SCS）计算热噪声功率，
        但实际应按<strong>单个 RB 带宽</strong>（12 &times; SCS）计算。
        对于 273 RB 的 100MHz 系统，噪声虚高 10&middot;log<sub>10</sub>(273) = <span style="color:#f87171;font-weight:600">24.4 dB</span>。</p>
    </div>
    <div class="challenge-section">
      <div class="challenge-section-label cause">&#x1F50D; 根因</div>
      <p>混淆了频域每 bin 的噪声功率与系统总噪声功率。每个频域 bin（RB）独立处理时，噪声带宽应为单 RB 宽度。</p>
    </div>
    <div class="challenge-section">
      <div class="challenge-section-label solution">&#x2705; 解决</div>
    </div>
    <div class="code-block">
      <span class="lang-label">Python</span>
      <code><span class="cm"># 修复前: bw_db = 10 * log10(self.bandwidth_hz)  # 系统总带宽!</span>
<span class="cm"># 修复后:</span>
bw_per_rb = <span class="num">12.0</span> * self.subcarrier_spacing  <span class="cm"># 单 RB 带宽</span>
bw_db = <span class="num">10.0</span> * math.log10(bw_per_rb)</code>
    </div>
    <div class="challenge-section">
      <div class="challenge-section-label result">&#x1F4CA; 效果</div>
      <p>QuaDRiGa NMSE 从 +29 dB 降至合理水平。Python / MATLAB / Sionna 三源全部同步修复。</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Challenge 2 -->
  <div class="challenge-card reveal">
    <div class="challenge-header">
      <span class="challenge-id">F-004</span>
      <span class="challenge-title">TDL 干扰功率与服务信道差 10 万倍</span>
    </div>
    <div class="challenge-section">
      <div class="challenge-section-label problem">&#x1F534; 问题</div>
      <p>Sionna RT 成功时服务信道功率极弱（3.4&times;10<sup>-9</sup>），而 TDL 生成的干扰信道原始功率 ~1-10。
        归一化后干扰比服务信道强 <span style="color:#f87171;font-weight:600">10 万倍</span>，
        SIR = -49.9 dB（应为正值）。</p>
    </div>
    <div class="challenge-section">
      <div class="challenge-section-label solution">&#x2705; 解决</div>
    </div>
    <div class="code-block">
      <span class="lang-label">Python</span>
      <code><span class="cm"># 将 TDL 干扰信道功率对齐到服务信道量级</span>
_h_tdl_pw = <span class="fn">float</span>(np.mean(np.abs(_h_tdl) ** <span class="num">2</span>))
_serv_pw = <span class="fn">float</span>(np.mean(np.abs(h_all[_s_idx]) ** <span class="num">2</span>))
<span class="kw">if</span> _h_tdl_pw > <span class="num">1e-30</span> <span class="kw">and</span> _serv_pw > <span class="num">1e-30</span>:
    _h_tdl = _h_tdl * np.sqrt(_serv_pw / _h_tdl_pw)</code>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Challenge 3 -->
  <div class="challenge-card reveal">
    <div class="challenge-header">
      <span class="challenge-id">F-008</span>
      <span class="challenge-title">时域相关缺失 — 相邻快照相关仅 0.13</span>
    </div>
    <div class="challenge-section">
      <div class="challenge-section-label problem">&#x1F534; 问题</div>
      <p>TDL 模型为每个时间快照独立生成信道，导致 3.6 km/h、10ms 间隔下相邻快照自相关系数仅
        <span style="color:#f87171;font-weight:600">0.13</span>，完全不符合物理衰落的 Jakes 自相关特性。</p>
    </div>
    <div class="challenge-section">
      <div class="challenge-section-label solution">&#x2705; 解决</div>
      <p>共享衰落状态：用确定性种子固定抽头增益和 Doppler 参数，在连续时间轴上评估 Sum-of-Sinusoids 模型。</p>
    </div>
    <div class="code-block">
      <span class="lang-label">Python</span>
      <code><span class="cm"># 连续时间轴 → Jakes 自相关 J₀(2π·f_d·Δt)</span>
t_axis = t_offset_s + np.arange(T) * T_sym
<span class="kw">for</span> n <span class="kw">in</span> range(N_sinusoids):
    phase += A_n * np.cos(<span class="num">2</span>*np.pi*f_d*t_axis*cos_theta_n + phi_n)
<span class="cm"># 衰落参数通过 fading_seed 跨快照共享</span></code>
    </div>
    <div class="challenge-section">
      <div class="challenge-section-label result">&#x1F4CA; 效果</div>
      <p>Lag-1 自相关从 <span style="color:#f87171">0.13</span> 提升至
        <span style="color:#4ade80;font-weight:600">0.88</span>（50 样本验证），符合 Jakes 理论预测。</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Challenge 4 -->
  <div class="challenge-card reveal">
    <div class="challenge-header">
      <span class="challenge-id">F-005</span>
      <span class="challenge-title">静态模式 UE 位置每帧随机漂移</span>
    </div>
    <div class="challenge-section">
      <div class="challenge-section-label problem">&#x1F534; 问题</div>
      <p>mobility_mode=static 时，8 个快照中 UE 位置出现离散跳变。静态模式本应位置完全不变。</p>
    </div>
    <div class="challenge-section">
      <div class="challenge-section-label cause">&#x1F50D; 根因</div>
      <p>静态模式不生成轨迹，每个快照的 <code>ue_pos_override=None</code>，RT 重试逻辑重新调用
        <code>_place_ues()</code> 导致位置重新随机化。</p>
    </div>
    <div class="challenge-section">
      <div class="challenge-section-label solution">&#x2705; 解决</div>
    </div>
    <div class="code-block">
      <span class="lang-label">Python</span>
      <code><span class="kw">if</span> self.mobility_mode == <span class="str">"static"</span>:
    static_rng = np.random.default_rng(self._seed + <span class="num">8888</span>)
    static_pos = self._place_ues(static_rng, sites, <span class="num">1</span>)[<span class="num">0</span>]
<span class="cm"># 所有快照共享同一 static_pos → max_position_delta = 0</span></code>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Challenge 5 -->
  <div class="challenge-card reveal">
    <div class="challenge-header">
      <span class="challenge-id">F-006</span>
      <span class="challenge-title">RT 失败回退破坏时间连续性</span>
    </div>
    <div class="challenge-section">
      <div class="challenge-section-label problem">&#x1F534; 问题</div>
      <p>Sionna RT 在序列中间某帧失败时，回退到独立 TDL 生成，导致该帧与前后帧完全不相关，
        时间序列断裂。</p>
    </div>
    <div class="challenge-section">
      <div class="challenge-section-label solution">&#x2705; 解决</div>
      <p>维护 <code>_last_rt_channels</code> 缓存，RT 失败时优先复用上一成功帧的信道数据。
        仅首帧（无历史记录）才降级到 TDL。这保持了时域连续性，同时不会在空间上引入错误。</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Challenge 6 -->
  <div class="challenge-card reveal">
    <div class="challenge-header">
      <span class="challenge-id">F-002</span>
      <span class="challenge-title">QuaDRiGa 零速度导致 MATLAB 崩溃</span>
    </div>
    <div class="challenge-section">
      <div class="challenge-section-label problem">&#x1F534; 问题</div>
      <p>静态模式下 <code>set_speed(0, T)</code> 导致 QuaDRiGa 内部 <code>samples_per_meter = Inf</code>，
        插值崩溃。同时静态/近静态轨迹返回的快照数少于请求数，reshape 出错。</p>
    </div>
    <div class="challenge-section">
      <div class="challenge-section-label solution">&#x2705; 解决</div>
      <p>双重保护：1) 速度地板值 <code>max(speed, 1e-3)</code> km/h 防止 Inf；
        2) 快照不足时 <code>repmat</code> 首帧填充到期望维度。</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Challenge 7 -->
  <div class="challenge-card reveal">
    <div class="challenge-header">
      <span class="challenge-id">ARCH</span>
      <span class="challenge-title">配对 UL/DL 干扰估计 — 1444 行大重构</span>
    </div>
    <div class="challenge-section">
      <div class="challenge-section-label problem">&#x1F534; 问题</div>
      <p>原始平台仅支持单链路(UL)估计，无法建模真实蜂窝系统中 UL 和 DL 方向各异的干扰特性。</p>
    </div>
    <div class="challenge-section">
      <div class="challenge-section-label solution">&#x2705; 解决 (5阶段)</div>
      <p><strong>Phase A</strong>: 扩展 ChannelSample 合约增加 <code>h_dl_*</code> 字段<br>
        <strong>Phase B</strong>: 共享 <code>_interference_estimation.py</code>：UL 用 ZC-SRS 叠加，DL 用 Gold-PRBS CSI-RS 叠加<br>
        <strong>Phase C</strong>: 三数据源全部适配 (internal_sim / sionna_rt / quadriga_real)<br>
        <strong>Phase D</strong>: Bridge 按方向拆分 Token (UL→SRS/DFT/RSRP, DL→PMI/CQI)<br>
        <strong>Phase E</strong>: FeatureExtractor 方向无关，无需改动<br>
        <span class="highlight--green">结果: 286 测试通过，13 跳过</span>
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Challenge 8 -->
  <div class="challenge-card reveal">
    <div class="challenge-header">
      <span class="challenge-id">INFRA</span>
      <span class="challenge-title">去 Dramatiq 化 — 消除外部依赖</span>
    </div>
    <div class="challenge-section">
      <div class="challenge-section-label problem">&#x1F534; 问题</div>
      <p>Dramatiq + Redis 消息队列在单进程模式下：Broker 实例冲突、ACK 残留导致消息丢失、依赖臃肿。</p>
    </div>
    <div class="challenge-section">
      <div class="challenge-section-label solution">&#x2705; 解决</div>
    </div>
    <div class="code-block">
      <span class="lang-label">Python</span>
      <code><span class="cm"># 线程直派，零外部依赖</span>
t = threading.Thread(
    target=_run_in_thread,
    args=(job_id, job_type, overrides),
    daemon=<span class="const">True</span>,
    name=<span class="str">f"job-{job_id[:8]}"</span>
)
t.start()
<span class="cm"># 失败时回退到 JSON 文件队列</span></code>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ========================= 11. TRUST ========================= -->
<section id="trust">
  <div class="reveal">
    <div class="section-label">Data Trust</div>
    <h2 class="section-title">数据可信度保障</h2>
    <p class="section-desc">三层防护体系确保从原始信道到最终 Embedding 的全链路数据质量。</p>
  </div>

  <div class="reveal">
    <div class="trust-layer trust-layer--l1">
      <h4>L1 — 数据合约 (Pydantic v2)</h4>
      <p>每个 ChannelSample 必须通过严格的 schema 校验：</p>
      <ul style="margin-top:8px; padding-left:20px; font-size:0.88rem; color:#94a3b8; line-height:2;">
        <li><strong>形状一致性</strong>: h_serving_true 必须为 [T, RB, BS_ant, UE_ant] 四维</li>
        <li><strong>类型约束</strong>: 信道矩阵必须为 complex64/complex128</li>
        <li><strong>范围校验</strong>: SNR ∈ [-30, 60] dB, SIR clamped to [-50, 50] dB</li>
        <li><strong>配对完整性</strong>: 若 paired_mode=true，则 h_dl_* 字段不可为 None</li>
        <li><strong>版本标记</strong>: CONTRACT_VERSION = "1.0"，确保前向兼容</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="trust-layer trust-layer--l2">
      <h4>L2 — 质量门控 (Quality Gates)</h4>
      <p>Bridge 阶段的三重自适应门控，每个 Gate 输出范围 [0.7, 1.0]：</p>
      <ul style="margin-top:8px; padding-left:20px; font-size:0.88rem; color:#94a3b8; line-height:2;">
        <li><strong>SINR Gate</strong>: 低 SINR 样本的 SRS 特征被软抑制 (×0.7)，而非丢弃</li>
        <li><strong>Energy Gate</strong>: SVD 奇异值权重反映每个空间层的信息量</li>
        <li><strong>PMI Gate</strong>: 基于 CQI 的预编码质量评估</li>
      </ul>
      <div class="formula-block mt-16" style="margin-bottom:0;">
        <span class="formula">gate = sigmoid(x) &times; 0.3 + 0.7 &nbsp;&#x2192;&nbsp; 永不完全关闭，保留信息下界</span>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="trust-layer trust-layer--l3">
      <h4>L3 — 评估闭环 (Evaluation Loop)</h4>
      <p>模型评估的三重保障：</p>
      <ul style="margin-top:8px; padding-left:20px; font-size:0.88rem; color:#94a3b8; line-height:2;">
        <li><strong>测试集锁定</strong>: 固定划分，不随训练数据变动</li>
        <li><strong>版本化</strong>: 每次评估记录数据版本、模型 checkpoint、超参数</li>
        <li><strong>6 指标综合</strong>: CT, TW, KNN, NMSE, Cosine, Kendall — 单一指标无法刷榜</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="card reveal mt-24">
    <h3>跨源一致性保障</h3>
    <p style="color:#94a3b8; font-size:0.88rem; margin-top:8px;">
      三个数据源共享同一 <code>ChannelSample</code> 合约 + 统一的功率归一化流程 + 一致的 TDD 方向互易处理。
      每次信道配置参数变更必须<strong>同步适配所有三个源</strong>（internal_sim / sionna_rt / quadriga_real），
      并同步更新前端 CollectWizard 和文档。这是团队通过多次跨源不一致 Bug 总结出的铁律。
    </p>
  </div>
</section>

